<div class="post">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 35px">F.A.Q. - Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            Are these official TF2 updates?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            No, they are completely created by TF2 community members and then rolled out to Creators.TF servers only.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            How can I play on the servers?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            View our list of servers at the <a href="/servers">servers</a> page. You can also search for the "creators" keyword in the TF2 community server browser.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            How can I get new items?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            You can get new items in the Mann Co. Work-Shop, located at the <a href="/store">Store page</a>. You can either buy items directly, or try your luck and open one of our crates!
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            Wait, this is all free?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            Yes! Everything in our servers is available to you, free of charge. With that being said, if you want to support our project, check out our <a href="/donate">Donation page</a>.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            How can I see my inventory?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            Visit the <a href="/my/inv">Items</a> tab on the header of the site.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            How do I complete contracts?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            Visit our <a href="/contracker">Contracker</a>, also available on the header of the site, select the contract you want to activate, and complete the objectives!
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            I have a different question, where do I ask?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            Either via email on <a href="mailto:support@creators.tf">support@creators.tf</a> or through our <a href="/discord" target="_blank">Discord</a> server.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faqquestionbox">
        <div class="faqquestion">
            IS IT FREE?
        </div>
        <div class="faqanswer">
            For the end user, yes. But, servers cost money, if you would like to donate and help with the server's cost, go to our <a href="/donate" target="_blank">Donation</a> page.
        </div>
    </div>
